B.alJ=new A.c("Diagram 1-1 shows part of the position from the static Rook versus ranging Rook game. White's King is in an odd square, but this actually happens when White plays Kx2b after Black's Bx2b+, Bishop exchange.")
B.afE=new A.c("Now is the good time for Black to drop a Knight, but where?")
