B.akv=new A.c("After White's K-3b, a natural move, Black goes on to play Nx3d. If White plays G-4a, B*2b will do. There'll be no stopping Black's Bx1a. If White plays G-3c, Black can still play B*2b. Then, Gx3d and Bx1a will follow, leading to a favorable position for Black.")
B.am6=new A.c("When you cannot drop a Knight where it can fork, see if you can drop it further back. You may come up with a smart move.")
