B.aiG=new A.c("Diagram 2-2 shows a similar position as Diagram 3. Again N*8f is a smart move. If you have a Pawn in hand, you can attack from the 9th file. If you have more pieces in hand, you can just play N-7d, mate.")
B.ajd=new A.c("Lastly let me show you how a Knight works in the edge attack.")
B.ME=new A.p("ln1g5/1ks1g4/1ppp5/p3p4/9/P1PP5/1P7/9/L8 b N2P","Diagram 2-3")
