B.alb=new A.c("The basic pattern of the edge attack begins with P-9e followed by P*9c.")
B.af4=new A.c("If you have more Pawns in hand, you can play P*9b before P*9c, which will give your opponent no choice.")
B.afo=new A.c("After luring White's Lance up to 9d, you play N*8f claiming the Lance. A very promising prospect on your part.")
B.alK=new A.c("When playing with the Mino-castle, you should remember that it is a sturdy castle when attacked from the side, but from the edge it could be pretty vulnerable.")
