B.ai6=new A.c("N-4e may give you a good feeling, momentarily. But White will then play S-4b, aiming at a later P*4d. That will be one Knight of yours that falls prey to a Pawn.")
B.anJ=new A.c("If Black did not have a Pawn on 5g, you could play N-4e. After S-4b, you can drop a P on 5d, thereby you can exchange your N for White's S in the future. Material gain means a lot in the beginning phase.")
B.akD=new A.c("Back on Diagram 1, you need to do something before playing N-4e. Which is...?")
