B.a8W=new A.O("Moves thereafter:",B.a5k,B.u)
B.aep=new A.c("After P*3c, if White responds with Bx3c or Gx3c, you can play N-4e forking the two pieces of higher value. What if White plays Nx3c? Yes, P*3d. You've learnt a lesson.")
