B.agD=new A.c("A flock of plovers in flight looks like cross-stitches. Hence, a Silver piece used like a plover refers to a move diagonally forward or rearward, rather than straight ahead.")
B.anz=new A.c("From Diagram 1 (last move K-3a), let me show you how you should redress the awkward positioning of the Silver in front of your Pawn.")
