B.anf=new A.c("You start with exchanging Pawns on the 3rd file, then play S-3g, and then S-3f so that you can next play N3g and B-4f, which will be an ideal position on your part. Not only is there no ill-positioned Silver in front of your Pawn, but all your pieces are prepared to attack.")
B.O7=new A.p("ln1g3nl/1ks1g1r2/1pp1psbpp/p2p1p3/6PP1/P1P1PS3/1P1P1P2P/1BKSG2R1/LN1G3NL b p","Diagram 3")
