B.ai0=new A.c("Sometimes it is a good idea to shift the Silver from right to left as in B depending on the opponent's move.")
B.aiV=new A.c("Remember that a Silver is like a midfielder moving swiftly around the mid-ranks in preparation for a major attack.")
