B.aiS=new A.c("From Diagram 2-2, White can play P-3f. Then there will be a Bishop-exchange followed by White's B*5e (Diagram 2-2). You may think White has gained the lead.")
B.LX=new A.p("lnsgkgsnl/6r2/pppppp1pp/9/4b2P1/2P3P2/PP1PPP2P/1S1K3R1/LN1G1GSNL b BP","Diagram 2-2")
