B.amT=new A.c("The proverb, literally meaning that Tokin is slow but fast, teaches that it may take time to drop a Pawn and promote it, but once you've made a Tokin, you may be surprised at how it gives impetus to the attack.")
B.an3=new A.c("Diagram 1-1 is from an actual game. White has dropped a Pawn on 4a blocking Black's Dragon's path. How would you play here?")
