B.aiH=new A.c("A Rook-exchange works for the ranging Rook side in many cases due to the safer castle. In other words, that is what you should aim for when you play ranging Rook. In preparation for that, you need to range your Rook to a crucial spot. So, where is the crucial spot? I will expound on that in the following section.")
