B.ahv=new A.c("When two of your pieces are attacked by one enemy piece with the same move, you cannot save both. This is not an uncommon situation when you play a quick attack opening like Yokofu-dori. The idea conveyed in the above proverb is: Don't just think of rescuing one of the threatened pieces, but consider the position in a positive light.")
